data.description: Welcome to this charming home, located in Fort Lawn. This three bedroom, two bathroom home is situated on just less than an acre. Two storage sheds will convey with the sale. Just far enough off Hwy 9 Bypass to enjoy the privacy, & lose enough to enjoy the nearby amenities! Perfect starter home!!!!
